members.member:
Clone an FSPANode and return it with a new shape ID

@param fspa
@param shapeID
@return

Some FSPANodes were adjusted mistakenly under the assumption that none of these images are part
of the text being inserted. This adjusts them back.

@param newFSPANodes is a list of the FSPANodes changed
@param length is how much they were adjusted 

